description:
The 3rd Fleet was a unit of the http://anidb.net/ch1535 [Free Planets] Star Fleet. By 796 UC, it was commanded by Vice Admiral http://anidb.net/ch772 [Lefebvre] with the flagship http://anidb.net/ch82271 [Cu Chulainn] and participated in the Alliance invasion of the http://anidb.net/ch1534 [Galactic Empire].
It was subsequently defeated and destroyed off the planet Lesing by the Wahlen Fleet prior to the Battle of Amritsar, in October of that year.
Source: Gineipaedia
name: Dai 3 Kantai
